description:
Maria Cadenzavna Eve is a spirited princess of song who reached the top of the American charts within two months from her professional debut. Her mysterious and powerful singing voice crosses international boundaries, and possesses large amounts fans around the world. She fuses with a Symphogear outside of the Japanese government`s jurisdiction, and takes actions worthy of making her an enemy to all humanity.
Source: ANN
name: Maria Cadenzavna Eve
